cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.MM

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image segmentation of plant leaves. The use of deep learning models also suggests that it could belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The mention of domain randomisation in the abstract suggests that it could also belong to the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. Finally, the use of synthetic images could suggest that it could belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
